{"tid":574808,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯電視台錯用遊戲畫面報導俄軍空襲敍利亞","createTime":"2018-02-27T17:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T06:04:27.000Z","uid":60545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a0cce57060a37b3e705d662cb935b2212fed3125","tid":574808,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯國營第一頻道電視台在一個節目中，錯誤利用一個電子遊戲的畫面，報道敍利亞戰況。雖然那個畫面只是持續了一秒，一閃即過，但仍引起觀眾注意，成為笑柄。<br />\n<br />\n該台在上星期日播出的一個節目中，向俄羅斯武裝部隊致敬，特別提到被視為戰爭英雄的戰機飛行員普羅倫科（Alexander Prokhorenko）。他有份在敍利亞古城巴爾米拉執行戰鬥任務，發現自己被伊斯蘭國武裝分子包圍，但他不顧安危，要求俄軍戰機向他所在的位置發動空襲。<br />\n<br />\n畫面顯示一批俄軍「SU-25」戰機執行轟炸任務，但心水清的觀眾和網民一眼便看出，其中有一秒畫面是來自2013年發行的電子遊戲《Arma 3》的。<br />\n<br />\n第一頻道電視台承認錯誤，指幕後人員剪接時，用錯了一個有關電子遊戲的舊片段的畫面。一名網民在社交網站留言道，這種情況已不是第一次發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1150358/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1150358%2F&d=MP5r6eUwNfSjSFn0NXIBn%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=14bf9331\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1150358%2F&h=3058ab78\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1150358/</a>"},{"pid":"2a7e345222cfd75d3842650cd5d22f6b5ab95c89","tid":574808,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T00:58:22.000Z","msg":"俄共同中共手法同出一切"},{"pid":"83a87ea10d57fd23bf9ac2e6addde381e46b8f9a","tid":574808,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1f01ed4a23bae85b7defaccc1e9f74bb3fbe95","tid":574808,"uid":7638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a7e345222cfd75d3842650cd5d22f6b5ab95c89","tid":574808,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T00:58:22.000Z","msg":"俄共同中共手法同出一切"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T06:04:27.000Z","msg":"諗起用高達設計圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}